        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">If you want to learn more, check out the book on Manning’s liveBook platform <a href="https://livebook.manning.com/book/graph-neural-networks-in-action?origin=product-look-inside&utm_source=medium&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=book_broadwater_graph_8_17_21" target="_self">here</a>.</p></div></div></div></section><?php include_once 'Elemental/footer.php'; ?>